{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. PALO ALTO HOUSE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There's a thunderstorm going on outside and rain is beating hard against the windows, DUSTIN, ANDREW-and the INTERNS are hard at work writing code.
